[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Schema is the only source of truth for your entire server.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] From request validation, type inference, OpenAPI documentation, client-server communication.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Every part of Elysia is design for complete type integrity.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia validates, and normalize requests against your schema, ensuring that only valid data reaches your handlers.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia also infers types directly from your schema, ensuring that your handlers always receive the correct types in both runtime, and type-level.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Every part of Elysia is designed to be completely type-safe far more advance type inference than any other frameworks.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia also infers type from your schema, provide an auto-completion for models or extends Elysia with your own custom property all while ensuring complete type integrity.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia can share types between client and server similar to tRPC, ensuring that both sides are always in sync.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Taking a step further, Elysia also handle multiple HTTP status and arrange them using discriminated union, allowing you to handle all possible error cases with ease.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia generates OpenAPI documentation from your schema in 1 line.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Ensuring your API documentation are always accurate and up-to-date.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia can generate OpenAPI specifications directly from your TypeScript code without any annotations, without any configuration and CLI running.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Allowing you to turn your actual code from any library like Prisma, Drizzle and every TypeScript library into your own API documentation.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] With seamless support for type inference, and OpenAPI.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia has 1st party support for OpenTelemetry.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Instrumentation is built-in, so you can easily monitor your services regardless of the platform.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Like tRPC, Elysia provides type-safety from the backend to the frontend without code generation.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] The interaction between frontend and backend is both type-checked at compile and runtime.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] Elysia provides a type-safe layer to interact with and test your server, from routes to parameters.
[src:elysia-bun/elysiajs-com] With auto-completion, you can easily write tests for the server without any hassle.
